name: #26. Atari Nakamoto
description:
Gamer, engineer, lepidopterist, lover. Holds the hi-scores on nearly every neighbourhood arcade machine. And the lady bunnies dig that. 


"What can travel all around the world without leaving its corner?"
"I have cities, but no houses. I have mountains, but no trees. I have water, but no fish. What am I?"
"The more of this there is, the less you see. What is it?"
"What has many teeth, but cannot bite?"
“Steve and Steve helped bring this classic to the world”

'r' toggles auto-rotate. ‘l’ toggles mouse following
